[{"id":22598,"type":2,"name":"花の詩女 ゴティックメード","name_cn":"GOTHICMADE 花之诗女","summary":"　　由永野护担任原作以及监督的长篇剧场版动画。\r\n　　《GOTHICMADE -花之诗女-》故事中被称为「诗女」的女性们，拥有能够传承记忆的特殊能力，而拥有这种特殊能力的她们，不但能加深民族、国家人们之间的羁绊，更能透过其言语将人类导向更好的未来。作品以新诞生的诗女，16 岁的少女「珼琳（ベリン）」作为主角，在她前往名为「哈里（ハリ）」的都市时，军事国家「多纳乌帝国（ドナウ帝国）」第三皇子便被分派成为珼琳的护卫。个性和思想上完全相反的两人，就此共同展开了旅程。\r\n　　而作为动画名称的「GOTHICMADE（简称为 GTM）」，则是被设定为史上最强的人型战斗兵器。而对於想要将「和平」传达给人们的珼琳来说，第三皇子所拥有的 GTM 可说是旅途中最大的障碍…。","date":"2012-11-01","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/d7/9b/22598_W8Kwk.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/d7/9b/22598_W8Kwk.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/d7/9b/22598_W8Kwk.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/d7/9b/22598_W8Kwk.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/d7/9b/22598_W8Kwk.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":19,"score":6.2,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":7,"6":2,"7":5,"8":0,"9":2,"10":1}},"tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":57},{"name":"2012","count":28},{"name":"永野护","count":20},{"name":"把五星的坑给填了啊","count":19},{"name":"萝卜","count":18},{"name":"永野護","count":12},{"name":"科幻","count":11},{"name":"想补的旧番","count":7},{"name":"机战","count":5},{"name":"漫画改","count":5},{"name":"大暴死","count":4}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":322,"collect":24,"doing":3,"on_hold":14,"dropped":12}},{"id":173816,"type":2,"name":"Dumb Ways To Die","name_cn":"蠢蠢的死法","summary":"　　墨尔本大都市公交铁路公司（Metro Trains）近日推出一则萌萌的公益广告叫做《呆呆的死法》，用以宣传铁路安全。http://dumbwaystodie.com/\r\n　　Melbourne’s metropolitan rail service, Metro, has released Dumb Ways To Die, a song to kick off their new campaign ","date":"2012-11-01","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/c6/73/173816_6R9kw.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/c6/73/173816_6R9kw.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/c6/73/173816_6R9kw.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/c6/73/173816_6R9kw.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/c6/73/173816_6R9kw.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":3962,"total":59,"score":6